<div class="w-full pb-16">
  <nav class="flex items-center justify-between py-5 border-b">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-green-700 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold">CA</div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-bold text-gray-900">Chama Agent</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Community operations, made accountable</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-green-800 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 px-3 py-2 rounded-full">
      OpenAI Build Week 2026
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center py-16">
    <div>
      <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-green-700 mb-4">
        Built for the groups that hold families together
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-6">
        Your mum's chama already runs on trust.
        <span class="text-green-700">We help it run with clarity.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-8">
        A chama is a member-run savings and investment group. Friends, relatives, neighbours, or colleagues contribute regularly—then use the shared fund for school fees, emergencies, small businesses, land, funerals, weddings, and a more secure future.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <%= link_to "Enter the live demo →",
                    chamas_path,
                    class: "bg-green-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-green-800 shadow-sm" %>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="border px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-50">
          See how it works
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <div class="absolute -inset-5 bg-green-50 rounded-3xl rotate-2"></div>
      <div class="relative bg-white border rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-7">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b pb-4 mb-5">
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500">Mum's chama</div>
            <div class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Umoja Women's Group</div>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs text-green-800 bg-green-50 px-3 py-2 rounded-full">12 members</span>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-green-800">Akinyi · 7:42 PM</div>
            <p class="text-gray-800 mt-1">I'll send my KES 5,000 tomorrow morning.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 ml-8">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600">Chairperson · 7:54 PM</div>
            <p class="text-gray-800 mt-1">Saturday: school-fees payout and late-payment policy.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border rounded-lg p-4 mt-5">
            <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
              <span class="text-gray-500">This month's pool</span>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">KES 60,000</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full h-2 bg-gray-100 rounded-full mt-3 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="h-full bg-green-700 rounded-full" style="width: 83%"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">10 of 12 members have contributed</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mb-16">
    <div class="bg-gray-900 text-white rounded-xl p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl font-bold">~12M</div>
      <div class="text-gray-300 mt-2">Kenyans estimated to participate in chamas</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-green-700 text-white rounded-xl p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl font-bold">~700M</div>
      <div class="text-green-100 mt-2">people estimated to use similar savings groups globally</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">1 promise</div>
      <div class="text-gray-600 mt-2">can affect a school term, an emergency, or a family's next investment</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="how-it-works" class="border rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-8">
      <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-green-700">From conversation to accountable action</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-3">The treasurer should not have to carry the whole group in her head.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <% [
        ["01", "Understand", "GPT-5.6 reads contribution records and exported group conversations."],
        ["02", "Organize", "Decisions, promises, owners, arrears, and unresolved issues become visible."],
        ["03", "Act", "Officials request contributions through M-PESA and send focused reminders."],
        ["04", "Account", "Live records and PDF statements give every member a shared source of truth."]
      ].each do |number, title, copy| %>
        <div>
          <div class="text-green-700 font-bold"><%= number %></div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mt-2"><%= title %></h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-2"><%= copy %></p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="text-center py-16">
    <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 mb-3">Known by different names. Built on the same trust.</p>
    <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Chama · Susu · Esusu · Tanda · Kye · ROSCA</p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">The local payment rail may change. The need to preserve decisions, coordinate contributions, and protect community trust does not.</p>
  </section>
</div>
